#. <section class="sutta" id="sn7.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Arahantavagga"
msgstr "1. The Perfected Ones"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Asurindakasutta"
msgstr "3. With Bharadvāja the Fiend"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.3:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrels’ feeding ground."

# This name must surely be an epithet, more intensive than Akkosaka, i.e. = “demon-lord”!
msgctxt "sn7.3:1.2"
msgid "Assosi kho asurindakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo:"
msgstr "The brahmin Bharadvāja the Fiend heard a rumor to the effect that:"

msgctxt "sn7.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"“bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo kira samaṇassa gotamassa santike agārasmā "
"anagāriyaṃ pabbajito”ti kupito anattamano yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ asabbhāhi pharusāhi vācāhi akkosati paribhāsati."
msgstr ""
"“A brahmin of the Bharadvāja clan has gone forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness in the presence of the ascetic Gotama!” Angry and displeased he "
"went to the Buddha and abused and insulted him with rude, harsh words."

msgctxt "sn7.3:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhagavā tuṇhī ahosi."
msgstr "But when he said this, the Buddha kept silent."

msgctxt "sn7.3:1.5"
msgid "Atha kho asurindakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then Bharadvāja the Fiend said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.3:1.6"
msgid "“jitosi, samaṇa, jitosi, samaṇā”ti."
msgstr "“You’re beaten, ascetic, you’re beaten!”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.3:2.1"
msgid "“Jayaṃ ve maññati bālo,"
msgstr "“‘Ha! I won!’ thinks the fool,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:2.2"
msgid "vācāya pharusaṃ bhaṇaṃ;"
msgstr "when speaking with harsh words."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:2.3"
msgid "Jayañcevassa taṃ hoti,"
msgstr "Patience is the true victory"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:2.4"
msgid "yā titikkhā vijānato."
msgstr "for those who understand."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.351"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.3:3.1"
msgid "Tasseva tena pāpiyo,"
msgstr "When you get angry at an angry person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:3.2"
msgid "yo kuddhaṃ paṭikujjhati;"
msgstr "you just make things worse for yourself."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:3.3"
msgid "Kuddhaṃ appaṭikujjhanto,"
msgstr "When you don’t get angry at an angry person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:3.4"
msgid "saṅgāmaṃ jeti dujjayaṃ."
msgstr "you win a battle hard to win."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.3:4.1"
msgid "Ubhinnamatthaṃ carati,"
msgstr "When you know that the other is angry,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:4.2"
msgid "attano ca parassa ca;"
msgstr "you act for the good of both"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:4.3"
msgid "Paraṃ saṅkupitaṃ ñatvā,"
msgstr "yourself and the other"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:4.4"
msgid "yo sato upasammati."
msgstr "if you’re mindful and stay calm."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.3:5.1"
msgid "Ubhinnaṃ tikicchantānaṃ,"
msgstr "People unskilled in Dhamma"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:5.2"
msgid "attano ca parassa ca;"
msgstr "consider one who heals both"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:5.3"
msgid "Janā maññanti bāloti,"
msgstr "oneself and the other"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.3:5.4"
msgid "ye dhammassa akovidā”ti."
msgstr "to be a fool.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.164"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.3:6.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, asurindakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Bharadvāja the Fiend said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.3:6.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! …” …"

msgctxt "sn7.3:6.3"
msgid "abbhaññāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn7.3:6.4"
msgid "Aññataro ca panāyasmā bhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosīti."
msgstr "And Venerable Bhāradvāja became one of the perfected."
